Description_lang: Your maximum health is increased by $s3% and every ${$s2/10} Rage you spend heals you for ${$s1/10}% of your maximum health.

description_blz.en_US: Your maximum health is increased by 6% and every 20 Rage you spend heals you for 1% of your maximum health.
